snippet.title: Freeland VR - A Massive Online VR World, Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Freeland VR! Meet people from all over the world, 
socialize and have fun, enjoy battles and challenges with your friends,
own land and build your personally designed property on a planet of your choice and more.

Kickstarter launching soon! 

Signup on our website to be the first to know when we launch our kickstarter and get the best prices: https://www.freelandvr.com

Join our Discord to be a part of the community and for early alpha testing: https://discord.gg/A7waxMb

DESIGN YOUR OWN PUBLIC SPACE
Build your personally designed property on a planet of your choice

CREATE DEEP CONNECTIONS
Create deep connections with people from all over the world, through otherworldly experiences

BECOME THE BEST
Challenge other players in racing, pvp or fight together in epic raids to find the real treasures of Freeland

Succesful pre-alpha testing has been done throughout 2020.

Check out our Facebook Page at: https://www.facebook.com/FreelandVR/
